comments: Hield (IND) brings his arm toward Thomas' BKN) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of Thomas' drive.
Nembhard (IND) and Sharpe (BKN) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Turner (IND) contests the layup attempt and marginal body contact occurs with Watanabe (BKN) after the release.
Watanabe (BKN) wraps Turner off ball.
Hield (IND) is moving alongside Thomas' (BKN) path and he avoids making contact with Thomas' arm as he defends the driving shot attempt.
Mills (BKN) does not put part of his hand under the ball, and either carry it from one point to another or bring it to a pause and then continue to dribble again.
Turner (IND) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without imminently actively guarding an opponent.
Hield (IND) is turning away from Thomas' (BKN) path as marginal body contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Morris (BKN) receives a technical foul for dead ball contact/physical taunt.
Haliburton (IND) extends his arm into Mills (BKN) and dislodges Mills from his legally obtained defensive position.
Mathurin (IND) brushes Mills' (BKN) arm and marginal contact occurs prior to Mills losing control of the ball.
Nembhard (IND) does not establish a legal guarding position in Sumner's (BKN) path prior to contact.
Haliburton (IND) is bracing for the contact from Sumner (BKN) and marginal contact occurs as Haliburton releases away from the contact.

Sumner (BKN) is called for a shooting foul when Haliburton (IND) lands on his foot during his jump shot attempt. The foul is reviewed as a potential flagrant foul and deemed to not meet the flagrant foul criteria because Haliburton overtly extended his leg forward to create the contact with Sumner. The shooting foul stood because whether the initial foul was on the correct player (or should have been a no call) is not a reviewable matter.
Mills (BKN) establishes his right foot as his pivot foot and he maintains his pivot foot after his gather.
Hield (IND) initiates contact with Mills' (BKN) arm as he attempts to tie up Mills.
Mills (BKN) avoids making contact with Hield (IND) as he defends the jump shot attempt.
Turner  (IND) commits a take foul on Sumner (BKN).
Watanabe (BKN) avoids making contact with Nembhard (IND) as he contests the jump shot attempt.
Morris (BKN) cleanly deflects the ball away from Mathurin (IND), and the ensuing body contact is marginal.
